Time Model Statistics

  • DB Time represents total time in user calls
  • DB CPU represents CPU time of foreground processes
  • Total CPU Time represents foreground and background processes
  • Statistics including the word "background" measure background process time, therefore do not contribute to the DB time statistic
  • Ordered by % of DB time in descending order, followed by Statistic Name

2pd8pp513tazwWITH runidname AS ( SELECT DISTINCT b.runid, a.jobname, a.jobtype, a.designprojectname, a.ismultiinstance FROM int_perf_np.int_jobexec_ht a INNER JOIN int_perf_np.int_jobrun_ht b ON ( a.jobid = b.jobid ) ), runrelatie AS ( SELECT b.controlling_runid AS runid_parent, b.runid AS runid_child, a.jobname, b.afg_runstarttimestamp FROM int_perf_np.int_jobexec_ht a INNER JOIN int_perf_np.int_jobrun_ht b ON ( a.jobid = b.jobid ) WHERE b.afg_runstarttimestamp BETWEEN TO_DATE('2024-01-01', 'yyyy-mm-dd') AND sysdate -- LET OP WE GEBRUIKEN NIET ALLES ANDERS WORD HET TE VEEL!!! AND b.controlling_runid IS NOT NULL -- voor een parent child relatie om te bepalen wat een "product" is heb je de extra rij voor product niet nodig... (deze rij word er later weer bij gefietst ), parent_child AS ( -- dit is de parent child lijst als input voor de hierarchy) SELECT runid_parent AS parent, runid_child AS child, jobname AS relatie_info FROM runrelatie ORDER BY afg_runstarttimestamp ), parent AS ( SELECT DISTINCT parent FROM parent_child ), child AS ( SELECT DISTINCT child FROM parent_child ), all_child_parent AS ( SELECT DISTINCT * FROM ( SELECT * FROM child UNION ALL SELECT * FROM parent ) ), relatie_type_tussenvorm AS ( SELECT parent AS persoon, 'Tussenvorm' AS relatie_type FROM parent INNER JOIN child ON child = parent ), relatie_type_product AS ( SELECT parent AS persoon, 'Product' AS relatie_type FROM parent LEFT JOIN child ON parent = child WHERE child IS NULL ), relatie_type_bron AS ( SELECT child AS persoon, 'Bron' AS relatie_type FROM parent right JOIN child ON parent = child WHERE parent IS NULL ), all_relatie_type AS ( SELECT persoon, relatie_type FROM relatie_type_bron UNION ALL SELECT persoon, relatie_type FROM relatie_type_tussenvorm UNION ALL SELECT persoon, relatie_type FROM relatie_type_product ), hierarchie AS ( -- de hierarchie bepalen met rijnummer en level SELECT ROWNUM AS rij, child, parent, level AS product_level FROM parent_child CONNECT BY NOCYCLE PRIOR child = parent ), hierarchie_tmp1 AS ( SELECT rij, child , parent, product_level, CASE WHEN product_level = 1 THEN parent ELSE NULL END AS product FROM hierarchie ORDER BY rij ), hierarchie_tmp2 AS ( -- eerste stap aanvullen prouduct veld!!! ) SELECT rij, child, parent, product_level, product, COUNT(product) OVER( ORDER BY rij ) AS x FROM hierarchie_tmp1 ), hierarchie_tmp3 AS ( -- tweede stap aanvullen prouduct veld!!! ) SELECT rij, child, parent, product_level, FIRST_VALUE(product) OVER(PARTITION BY x ORDER BY rij ) AS product FROM hierarchie_tmp2 ), hierarchie_tmp4 AS ( SELECT h.rij, h.child, h.parent, h.product_level, h.product FROM hierarchie_tmp3 h INNER JOIN relatie_type_product p ON ( h.product = p.persoon ) ORDER BY rij ), hierarchie_tmp5 AS ( -- EXTRA 0 level niveau erbij. Hier gebruiken we de 0 velden die al bestaan in de gegevens. De velden waar de parent NULL is. DEZE MOET NOG STANDAARD LAATSTE VELD WORDEN SELECT TO_NUMBER('0') AS rij, runid AS child, runid AS parent, TO_NUMBER('0') AS product_level, runid AS product FROM int_perf_np.int_jobexec_ht a INNER JOIN int_perf_np.int_jobrun_ht b ON ( a.jobid = b.jobid ) WHERE b.afg_runstarttimestamp BETWEEN TO_DATE('2024-01-01', 'yyyy-mm-dd') AND sysdate AND b.controlling_runid IS NULL ), hierarchie_tmp6 AS ( -- de laatste hierarchie_tmp4 en hierarchie_tmp5 samenvoegen) SELECT rij, child, parent, product_level, product FROM hierarchie_tmp4 UNION ALL SELECT rij, child, parent, product_level, product FROM hierarchie_tmp5 ), kerstboom AS ( SELECT h.rij, h.product AS product_id, x.jobname AS product_naam, x1.relatie_type AS product_relatie_type, h.product_level, h.parent AS parent_id, y.jobname AS parent_naam, x2.relatie_type AS parent_relatie_type, h.child AS child_id, z.jobname AS child_naam, x3.relatie_type AS child_relatie_type, z.jobtype AS child_jobtype, z.designprojectname AS child_designprojectname, z.ismultiinstance AS child_ismultiinstance FROM hierarchie_tmp6 h JOIN runidname x ON ( h.product = x.runid ) JOIN runidname y ON ( h.parent = y.runid ) JOIN runidname z ON ( h.child = z.runid ) JOIN all_relatie_type x1 ON ( h.product = x1.persoon ) JOIN all_relatie_type x2 ON ( h.parent = x2.persoon ) JOIN all_relatie_type x3 ON ( h.child = x3.persoon ) ), kerstboom_ext1 AS ( -- alle runs zijn uniek dus je hoeft per runid alle data bij te voegen en je hebt alle extra gegevens... MIOSSCHIEN NOG WAT EXTRA INFO ZOALS INVOCATION INFO SELECT k.rij, k.product_id, k.product_naam, k.product_relatie_type, k.product_level, k.parent_id, k.parent_naam, k.parent_relatie_type, k.child_id, k.child_naam, k.child_relatie_type, k.child_jobtype, k.child_designprojectname, k.child_ismultiinstance, r.invocationid, r.runstarttimestamp, r.runendtimestamp, r.afg_runstarttimestamp, r.afg_runendtimestamp, r.runtype, r.runmajorstatus, r.runminorstatus, r.elapsedrunsecs, r.totalrowsconsumed, r.totalrowsproduced, r.totalcpu FROM kerstboom k INNER JOIN int_perf_np.int_jobrun_ht r ON ( k.child_id = r.runid ) ), run_start_end_1 AS ( -- alle kerstboomen de start en eind in 2 regels stoppen!! Deze heeft de start SELECT rij, product_id, product_naam, product_relatie_type, product_level, parent_id, parent_naam, parent_relatie_type, child_id, child_naam, child_relatie_type, child_jobtype, child_designprojectname, child_ismultiinstance, invocationid, runstarttimestamp, runendtimestamp, runtype, runmajorstatus, runminorstatus, elapsedrunsecs, totalrowsconsumed, totalrowsproduced, totalcpu, afg_runstarttimestamp AS run_startend, 'start' AS startstop, 1 AS verander FROM kerstboom_ext1 ), run_start_end_2 AS ( -- alle kerstboomen de start en eind in 2 regels stoppen!! Deze heeft de stop SELECT rij, product_id, product_naam, product_relatie_type, product_level, parent_id, parent_naam, parent_relatie_type, child_id, child_naam, child_relatie_type, child_jobtype, child_designprojectname, child_ismultiinstance, invocationid, runstarttimestamp, runendtimestamp, runtype, runmajorstatus, runminorstatus, elapsedrunsecs, totalrowsconsumed, totalrowsproduced, totalcpu, afg_runendtimestamp AS run_startend, 'stop' AS startstop, - 1 AS verander FROM kerstboom_ext1 ), run_start_end_all AS ( -- DIT IS DE BASIS, VANAF HIER ALLEEN NOG EXTRA SOMMATIES BIJVOEGEN OP VERSCH ILLENDE NIVEAUS.. SELECT * FROM run_start_end_1 UNION ALL SELECT * FROM run_start_end_2 ), sum_all AS ( -- 3. som aantal draaiende jobs op alles geordenend naar tijd (dus over de modules heen) SELECT rij, product_id, product_naam, product_relatie_type, product_level, parent_id, parent_naam, parent_relatie_type, child_id, child_naam, child_relatie_type, child_jobtype, child_designprojectname, child_ismultiinstance, 32xr8ga10bp0kDECLARE osUser VARCHAR2(30); osProgram VARCHAR2(200); dfTablespace varchar2(50); dfProfile varchar(50); BEGIN IF ora_login_user IS NULL THEN RETURN; END IF; SELECT OSUSER, program INTO osUser, osProgram FROM V$SESSION WHERE SID = SYS_CONTEXT('USERENV', 'SID'); select lower(default_tablespace), profile into dfTablespace, dfProfile from dba_users where username = ora_login_user; if lower(osUser) in ('dsadm', 'oracle', 'root', 'grid') or dfTablespace in ('users', 'xmetaspace', 'iaspace', 'xmetasrspace', 'microservicespace', 'dsodbspace', 'qssrdspace') or osProgram in ('Toad.exe') then return; elsif (dfProfile in ('BO_PROFILES', 'PBI_PROFILES') )--and REGEXP_LIKE(upper(osUser), '^[A-Z]{3}[0-9]{3}$')) then return; else RAISE_APPLICATION_ERROR(-20000, 'Logon Denied for user '||ora_login_user||' with os user '||osUser); end if; end;

b.datum_ontvangstaanvraag , b.awb_startdatum , b.proces_startdatum , b.awb_einddatum , b.afg_reden_einde , b.code_klanttype , b.code_soort_recht , b.uitkomst , w.ind_afgewezen_wajong , b.smf_casus_id , b.ind_casus_bz_internationaal , b.ger_einddatum_va_ad_ind from beoordeling b left outer join afgewezen_wajong w on w.pcs_id = b.pcs_id order by b.pcs_id
38ncj2h3sat9dMERGE /*+ INDEX(dest (signature category obj_type plan_id)) */ INTO sqlobj$ dest USING (SELECT :1 signature, :2 category, :3 obj_type, :4 plan_id FROM dual) src ON (dest.signature = src.signature AND dest.category = src.category AND dest.obj_type = src.obj_type AND dest.plan_id = src.plan_id) WHEN MATCHED THEN UPDATE SET name = :5, flags = :6, last_executed = :7 WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN INSERT (signature, category, obj_type, plan_id, name, flags, last_executed) VALUES (:8, :9, :10, :11, :12, :13, :14)

3pkuhx6dpucn4WITH runidname AS ( SELECT DISTINCT b.runid, a.jobname, a.jobtype, a.designprojectname, a.ismultiinstance FROM int_perf_np.int_jobexec_ht a INNER JOIN int_perf_np.int_jobrun_ht b ON ( a.jobid = b.jobid ) ), runrelatie AS ( SELECT b.controlling_runid AS runid_parent, b.runid AS runid_child, a.jobname, b.afg_runstarttimestamp FROM int_perf_np.int_jobexec_ht a INNER JOIN int_perf_np.int_jobrun_ht b ON ( a.jobid = b.jobid ) WHERE b.afg_runstarttimestamp BETWEEN TO_DATE('2024-01-01', 'yyyy-mm-dd') AND sysdate -- LET OP WE GEBRUIKEN NIET ALLES ANDERS WORD HET TE VEEL!!! AND b.controlling_runid IS NOT NULL -- voor een parent child relatie om te bepalen wat een "product" is heb j e de extra rij voor product niet nodig... (deze rij word er later weer bij gefietst ), parent_child AS ( -- dit is de parent child lijst als input voor de hierarchy) SELECT runid_parent AS parent, runid_child AS child, jobname AS relatie_info FROM runrelatie ORDER BY afg_runstarttimestamp ), parent AS ( SELECT DISTINCT parent FROM parent_child ), child AS ( SELECT DISTINCT child FROM parent_child ), all_child_parent AS ( SELECT DISTINCT * FROM ( SELECT * FROM child UNION ALL SELECT * FROM parent ) ), relatie_type_tussenvorm AS ( SELECT parent AS persoon, 'Tussenvorm' AS relatie_type FROM parent INNER JOIN child ON child = parent ), relatie_type_product AS ( SELECT parent AS persoon, 'Product' AS relatie_type FROM parent LEFT JOIN child ON parent = child WHERE child IS NULL ), relatie_type_bron AS ( SELECT child AS persoon, 'Bron' AS relatie_type FROM parent right JOIN child ON parent = child WHERE parent IS NULL ), all_relatie_type AS ( SELECT persoon, relatie_type FROM relatie_type_bron UNION ALL SELECT persoon, relatie_type FROM relatie_type_tussenvorm UNION ALL SELECT persoon, relatie_type FROM relatie_type_product ), hierarchie AS ( -- de hierarchie bepalen met rijnummer en level SELECT ROWNUM AS rij, child, parent, level AS product_level FROM parent_child CONNECT BY NOCYCLE PRIOR child = parent ), hierarchie_tmp1 AS ( SELECT rij, chi ld, parent, product_level, CASE WHEN product_level = 1 THEN parent ELSE NULL END AS product FROM hierarchie ORDER BY rij ), hierarchie_tmp2 AS ( -- eerste stap aanvullen prouduct veld!!! ) SELECT rij, child, parent, product_level, product, COUNT(product) OVER( ORDER BY rij ) AS x FROM hierarchie_tmp1 ), hierarchie_tmp3 AS ( -- tweede stap aanvullen prouduct veld!!! ) SELECT rij, child, parent, product_level, FIRST_VALUE(product) OVER(PARTITION BY x ORDER BY rij ) AS product FROM hierarchie_tmp2 ), hierarchie_tmp4 AS ( SELECT h.rij, h.child, h.parent, h.product_level, h.product FROM hierarchie_tmp3 h INNER JOIN relatie_type_product p ON ( h.product = p.persoon ) ORDER BY rij ), hierarchie_tmp5 AS ( -- EXTRA 0 level niveau erbij. cjf5nygc4mqkyWITH runidname AS ( SELECT DISTINCT b.runid, a.jobname, a.jobtype, a.designprojectname, a.ismultiinstance FROM int_perf_np.int_jobexec_ht a INNER JOIN int_perf_np.int_jobrun_ht b ON ( a.jobid = b.jobid ) ), runrelatie AS ( SELECT b.controlling_runid AS runid_parent, b.runid AS runid_child, a.jobname, b.afg_runstarttimestamp FROM int_perf_np.int_jobexec_ht a INNER JOIN int_perf_np.int_jobrun_ht b ON ( a.jobid = b.jobid ) WHERE b.afg_runstarttimestamp BETWEEN TO_DATE('2024-01-01', 'yyyy-mm-dd') AND sysdate -- LET OP WE GEBRUIKEN NIET ALLES ANDERS WORD HET TE VEEL!!! AND b.controlling_runid IS NOT NULL -- voor een parent child relatie om te bepalen wat een "product" is heb j e de extra rij voor product niet nodig... (deze rij word er later weer bij gefietst ), parent_child AS ( -- dit is de parent child lijst als input voor de hierarchy) SELECT runid_parent AS parent, runid_child AS child, jobname AS relatie_info FROM runrelatie ORDER BY afg_runstarttimestamp ), parent AS ( SELECT DISTINCT parent FROM parent_child ), child AS ( SELECT DISTINCT child FROM parent_child ), all_child_parent AS ( SELECT DISTINCT * FROM ( SELECT * FROM child UNION ALL SELECT * FROM parent ) ), relatie_type_tussenvorm AS ( SELECT parent AS persoon, 'Tussenvorm' AS relatie_type FROM parent INNER JOIN child ON child = parent ), relatie_type_product AS ( SELECT parent AS persoon, 'Product' AS relatie_type FROM parent LEFT JOIN child ON parent = child WHERE child IS NULL ), relatie_type_bron AS ( SELECT child AS persoon, 'Bron' AS relatie_type FROM parent right JOIN child ON parent = child WHERE parent IS NULL ), all_relatie_type AS ( SELECT persoon, relatie_type FROM relatie_type_bron UNION ALL SELECT persoon, relatie_type FROM relatie_type_tussenvorm UNION ALL SELECT persoon, relatie_type FROM relatie_type_product ), hierarchie AS ( -- de hierarchie bepalen met rijnummer en level SELECT ROWNUM AS rij, child, parent, level AS product_level FROM parent_child CONNECT BY NOCYCLE PRIOR child = parent ), hierarchie_tmp1 AS ( SELECT rij, chi ld, parent, product_level, CASE WHEN product_level = 1 THEN parent ELSE NULL END AS product FROM hierarchie ORDER BY rij ), hierarchie_tmp2 AS ( -- eerste stap aanvullen prouduct veld!!! ) SELECT rij, child, parent, product_level, product, COUNT(product) OVER( ORDER BY rij ) AS x FROM hierarchie_tmp1 ), hierarchie_tmp3 AS ( -- tweede stap aanvullen prouduct veld!!! ) SELECT rij, child, parent, product_level, FIRST_VALUE(product) OVER(PARTITION BY x ORDER BY rij ) AS product FROM hierarchie_tmp2 ), hierarchie_tmp4 AS ( SELECT h.rij, h.child, h.parent, h.product_level, h.product FROM hierarchie_tmp3 h INNER JOIN relatie_type_product p ON ( h.product = p.persoon ) ORDER BY rij ), hierarchie_tmp5 AS ( -- EXTRA 0 level niveau erbij. Hier gebruiken we de 0 velden die al bestaan in de gegevens. De velden waar de parent NULL is. Findings and Recommendations
----------------------------

Finding 1: Top SQL Statements
Impact is .51 active sessions, 31.96% of total activity.
--------------------------------------------------------
SQL statements consuming significant database time were found. These
statements offer a good opportunity for performance improvement.

Recommendation 1: SQL Tuning
Estimated benefit is .26 active sessions, 16.25% of total activity.
-------------------------------------------------------------------
Action
Run SQL Tuning Advisor on the SELECT statement with SQL_ID
"2pd8pp513tazw".
Related Object
SQL statement with SQL_ID 2pd8pp513tazw.
WITH runidname AS (
SELECT DISTINCT
b.runid,
a.jobname,
a.jobtype,
a.designprojectname,
a.ismultiinstance
FROM
int_perf_np.int_jobexec_ht a
INNER JOIN int_perf_np.int_jobrun_ht b ON ( a.jobid = b.jobid )
), runrelatie AS (
SELECT
b.controlling_runid AS runid_parent,
b.runid             AS runid_child,
a.jobname,
b.afg_runstarttimestamp
FROM
int_perf_np.int_jobexec_ht a
INNER JOIN int_perf_np.int_jobrun_ht b ON ( a.jobid = b.jobid )
WHERE
b.afg_runstarttimestamp BETWEEN TO_DATE('2024-01-01', 'yyyy-mm-dd')
AND sysdate    -- LET OP WE GEBRUIKEN NIET ALLES ANDERS WORD HET TE
VEEL!!!
AND b.controlling_runid IS NOT NULL  -- voor een parent child relatie
om te bepalen wat een "product" is heb je de extra rij voor product
niet nodig... (deze rij word er later weer bij gefietst
), parent_child AS (  -- dit is de parent child lijst als input voor
de hierarchy)
SELECT
runid_parent AS parent,
runid_child  AS child,
jobname      AS relatie_info
FROM
runrelatie
ORDER BY
afg_runstarttimestamp
), parent AS (
SELECT DISTINCT
parent
FROM
parent_child
), child AS (
SELECT DISTINCT
child
FROM
parent_child
), all_child_parent AS (
SELECT DISTINCT
*
FROM
(
SELECT
*
FROM
child
UNION ALL
SELECT
*
FROM
parent
)
), relatie_type_tussenvorm AS (
SELECT
parent       AS persoon,
'Tussenvorm' AS relatie_type
FROM
parent
INNER JOIN child ON child = parent
), relatie_type_product AS (
SELECT
parent    AS persoon,
'Product' AS relatie_type
FROM
parent
LEFT JOIN child ON parent = child
WHERE
child IS NULL
), relatie_type_bron AS (
SELECT
child  AS persoon,
'Bron' AS relatie_type
FROM
parent right
JOIN child ON parent = child
WHERE
parent IS NULL
), all_relatie_type AS (
SELECT
persoon,
relatie_type
FROM
relatie_type_bron
UNION ALL
SELECT
persoon,
relatie_type
FROM
relatie_type_tussenvorm
UNION ALL
SELECT
persoon,
relatie_type
FROM
relatie_type_product
), hierarchie AS (   -- de hierarchie bepalen met rijnummer en level
SELECT
ROWNUM AS rij,
child,
parent,
level  AS product_level
FROM
parent_child
CONNECT BY NOCYCLE
PRIOR child = parent
), hierarchie_tmp1 AS (
SELECT
rij,
child,
parent,
product_level,
CASE
WHEN product_level = 1 THEN
parent
ELSE
NULL
END AS product
FROM
hierarchie
ORDER BY
rij
), hierarchie_tmp2 AS ( -- eerste stap aanvullen prouduct veld!!! )
SELECT
rij,
child,
parent,
product_level,
product,
COUNT(product)
OVER(
ORDER BY
rij
) AS x
FROM
hierarchie_tmp1
), hierarchie_tmp3 AS ( -- tweede stap aanvullen prouduct veld!!! )
SELECT
rij,
child,
parent,
product_level,
FIRST_VALUE(product)
OVER(PARTITION BY x
ORDER BY
rij
) AS product
FROM
hierarchie_tmp2
), hierarchie_tmp4 AS (
SELECT
h.rij,
h.child,
h.parent,
h.product_level,
h.product
FROM
hierarchie_tmp3 h

DIM_START_DATUM_HUB, CAST(BALOP_5.DIM_EIND_DATUM AS TIMESTAMP(6)) as
DIM_EIND_DATUM, CAST(BALOP_5.DIM_KEY_BRZ AS NUMBER(19)) as
DIM_KEY_BRZ, CAST(BALOP_5.DIM_STATUS AS VARCHAR2(9)) as DIM_STATUS,
CAST(BALOP_5.DIM_ACTIE AS VARCHAR2(9)) as DIM_ACTIE,
CAST(BALOP_5.DIM_RECENT_IND AS CHAR(1)) as DIM_RECENT_IND
from
(select STG_DIM_HUB_KEY as DIM_HUB_KEY, STG_DIM_MD5 as DIM_MD5,
DIM_START_DATUM as DIM_START_DATUM, DIM_START_DATUM_HUB as
DIM_START_DATUM_HUB, DIM_EIND_DATUM as DIM_EIND_DATUM, DIM_KEY_BRZ as
DIM_KEY_BRZ, DIM_STATUS as DIM_STATUS,  CASE WHEN (DIM_KEY_BRZ is
null ) THEN ('I') WHEN (RIJ_NR > 1) THEN ('I') WHEN (((DIM_KEY_BRZ is
not null ) and (BRZ_DIM_MD5 <> STG_DIM_MD5)) and (DIM_STATUS is null
)) THEN ('U') WHEN (((DIM_KEY_BRZ is not null ) and (BRZ_DIM_MD5 =
STG_DIM_MD5)) and (DIM_STATUS = 'S')) THEN ('USX') WHEN
(((DIM_KEY_BRZ is not null ) and (BRZ_DIM_MD5 <> STG_DIM_MD5)) and
(DIM_STATUS = 'S')) THEN ('USI') WHEN (((DIM_KEY_BRZ is not null )
and (BRZ_DIM_MD5 = STG_DIM_MD5)) and (DIM_STATUS = 'H')) THEN ('UHX')
WHEN (((DIM_KEY_BRZ is not null ) and (BRZ_DIM_MD5 <> STG_DIM_MD5))
and (DIM_STATUS = 'H')) THEN ('UHI') ELSE ('X') END as DIM_ACTIE,
CASE WHEN (RIJ_NR_TOTAAL = RIJ_NR) THEN ('J') ELSE ('N') END as
DIM_RECENT_IND
from
(select BALOP_1.DIM_HUB_KEY as STG_DIM_HUB_KEY, BALOP_3.DIM_MD5 as
BRZ_DIM_MD5, BALOP_1.STG_DIM_MD5 as STG_DIM_MD5,
BALOP_1.DIM_START_DATUM as DIM_START_DATUM, BALOP_1.DIM_EIND_DATUM as
DIM_EIND_DATUM, BALOP_3.DIM_KEY_BRZ as DIM_KEY_BRZ,
BALOP_3.DIM_STATUS as DIM_STATUS, BALOP_1.RIJ_NR as RIJ_NR,
BALOP_1.RIJ_NR_TOTAAL as RIJ_NR_TOTAAL, BALOP_3.DIM_START_DATUM_HUB
as DIM_START_DATUM_HUB
from
(select  row_number() over (partition by DIM_HUB_KEY order by
DIM_START_DATUM) as rij_nr,
dim_hub_key,
dim_md5 as stg_dim_md5,
dim_start_datum,
lead(STG_actie_HUB_TB.dim_start_datum,1,date'9999-12-31') over
(partition by STG_actie_HUB_TB.dim_hub_key order by
STG_actie_HUB_TB.dim_start_datum asc)
as dim_eind_datum,
count(*) over (partition by DIM_HUB_KEY)  as RIJ_NR_TOTAAL
from stg_resafasa.STG_actie_HUB_TB) BALOP_1
left outer join
(select DIM_HUB_KEY as DIM_HUB_KEY, DIM_MD5 as DIM_MD5, DIM_KEY_BRZ
as DIM_KEY_BRZ, DIM_STATUS as DIM_STATUS, DIM_START_DATUM as
DIM_START_DATUM_HUB
from brz_resafasa.BRZ_actie_HUB_HT BRZ_actie_HUB_HT
where DIM_RECENT_IND = 'J') BALOP_3
on ((BALOP_1.DIM_HUB_KEY = BALOP_3.DIM_HUB_KEY) or
((BALOP_1.DIM_HUB_KEY is null ) and (BALOP_3.DIM_HUB_KEY is null )))
order by BALOP_1.DIM_HUB_KEY asc nulls first ) BALOP_4
where  CASE WHEN (DIM_KEY_BRZ is null ) THEN ('I') WHEN (RIJ_NR > 1)
THEN ('I') WHEN (((DIM_KEY_BRZ is not null ) and (BRZ_DIM_MD5 <>
STG_DIM_MD5)) and (DIM_STATUS is null )) THEN ('U') WHEN
(((DIM_KEY_BRZ is not null ) and (BRZ_DIM_MD5 = STG_DIM_MD5)) and
(DIM_STATUS = 'S')) THEN ('USX') WHEN (((DIM_KEY_BRZ is not null )
and (BRZ_DIM_MD5 <> STG_DIM_MD5)) and (DIM_STATUS = 'S')) THEN
('USI') WHEN (((DIM_KEY_BRZ is not null ) and (BRZ_DIM_MD5 =
STG_DIM_MD5)) and (DIM_STATUS = 'H')) THEN ('UHX') WHEN
(((DIM_KEY_BRZ is not null ) and (BRZ_DIM_MD5 <> STG_DIM_MD5)) and
(DIM_STATUS = 'H')) THEN ('UHI') ELSE ('X') END <> 'X') BALOP_5
